{"tid":190531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"色不是「空」　日內瓦修改百年禁令：女性可裸上身游泳","createTime":"2017-04-07T07:30:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T11:56:56.000Z","uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"808365d23bb8ee1adb90e5a77554af856bd6b9c4","tid":190531,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T07:30:57.000Z","msg":"2017年04月7日 13:40<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2441/d2441705.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2441%2Fd2441705.jpg&h=525a95b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲日內瓦日解放百年禁令：女性可以合法裸上身戲水。(徑意圖／翻攝自網路) <br />\n<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n瑞士日內瓦區議會日前修改了近百年的比堅尼泳衣禁令：裁定婦女可以在日內瓦湖及羅訥河(river Rh&ocirc;ne)合法祼上身戲水，不再有遭到罰款的下場。<br />\n<br />\n有233名當地居民簽署請願書要求修法，最終說服了立法者。區議會投票決定修改1929年禁止婦女在城市自然水域游泳的法例，但此這一改變並不適用於公共泳池。<br />\n<br />\n上述議題去年夏天在當地成為頭條新聞，起緣於 一名女子因為上空游泳而遭到罰款。她提出抗議：女性裸上身曬日光浴為何又不會受罰？這好比魚的眼睛比過路人的眼睛需要更多的遮蔽，實在說不過去！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170407/899544.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20170407%2F899544.htm&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGoi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=0b955486\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170407/899544.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e4c97b8651a80645de5ec53e067e54e93d622674","tid":190531,"uid":66494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T07:43:20.000Z","msg":"組隊去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c48648362d6c0f8aea5c022b04e9acedd8372bb","tid":190531,"uid":84043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T07:48:19.000Z","msg":"一定好多老女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47cfc078d9f24dea22d59786912f47517082904d","tid":190531,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T08:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5314c9787e882668f4852437f